  <brief_title>A Study to Assess Virtual Reality by Healthcare Providers to Improve Focus and Reduce Anxiety</brief_title>
  <official_title>Acceptability of Virtual Reality Experience by Health Care Providers for Improving Focus and Reducing Anxiety: A Pilot Trial</official_title>
